斗争的发展，不可","box":[[214,2726],[2022,2712],[2022,2756],[214,2770]]},{"text":"1972年第7期","box":[[214,2844],[503,2844],[503,2880],[214,2880]]},{"text":"（总559）·5","box":[[1732,2836],[2007,2832],[2008,2869],[1733,2873]]}],"dimensions":{"height":3317,"width":2638}}